[thunder booms]

00:48:49.177 --> 00:48:50.637
[rain patters]

00:48:50.720 --> 00:48:52.555
It's--it's raining.

00:48:52.639 --> 00:48:55.183
It's raining.
Dad!

00:48:55.266 --> 00:48:57.477
Oh no--no--no!

