It's not raining, is it?

00:49:09.447 --> 00:49:12.117
[gasping]

00:49:15.245 --> 00:49:16.579
[radio clicks]
Yes, it is.

00:49:16.663 --> 00:49:19.040
<i>[rain pattering]</i>

00:49:22.085 --> 00:49:24.003
Mom, the temperature
is dropping.

00:49:26.297 --> 00:49:28.258
No!

00:49:28.341 --> 00:49:30.135
Give me the magnesium.

00:49:30.218 --> 00:49:32.679
[thunder rumbles]

00:49:34.472 --> 00:49:37.475
[lighter clicks, flicking]

00:49:39.727 --> 00:49:41.646
Damn it!
[alarm beeps]

00:49:47.527 --> 00:49:48.695
[radio beeps]

00:49:48.778 --> 00:49:50.530
<i>We're gonna get you out.</i>

00:49:50.613 --> 00:49:53.283
[sobbing]

00:49:53.366 --> 00:49:55.410
She's <i>strong.
[sobbing]</i>

00:49:55.493 --> 00:49:58.121
She has more time.

00:49:58.204 --> 00:50:00.415
Dig!

00:50:00.498 --> 00:50:03.418
Come on!

00:50:05.128 --> 00:50:06.588
I'm coming, baby!

00:50:15.513 --> 00:50:17.223
[grunts]

00:50:19.350 --> 00:50:21.728
[panicked breaths]

00:50:30.653 --> 00:50:32.405
Dad.

00:50:32.488 --> 00:50:35.241
Dad, come in.

00:50:35.325 --> 00:50:38.161
Dad, there's a fire and...

00:50:38.244 --> 00:50:41.164
and I can't get out.

00:50:43.249 --> 00:50:44.542
Dad.

00:50:44.626 --> 00:50:46.252
[radio beeps]
Dad, come in.

00:50:59.390 --> 00:51:02.310
[stomping]

00:51:02.393 --> 00:51:05.313
<i>[forlorn music]</i>

00:51:15.740 --> 00:51:18.117
[mechanical humming]

00:51:34.759 --> 00:51:37.345
[mechanical thrumming]

00:51:51.317 --> 00:51:53.319
No point in you dying too.

00:52:06.416 --> 00:52:08.376
[wood creaks]

00:52:10.378 --> 00:52:13.172
[metallic thud]

00:52:26.019 --> 00:52:28.354
[sighs]

00:52:37.739 --> 00:52:41.242
[crying]

00:52:49.375 --> 00:52:52.295
<i>[triumphant music]</i>

00:53:24.494 --> 00:53:26.287
Thanks.

00:53:38.674 --> 00:53:41.594
<i>[ominous music]</i>

00:53:46.349 --> 00:53:49.394
[mechanical clanking]

00:53:53.481 --> 00:53:56.025
All: [grunting]

00:53:58.027 --> 00:54:00.446
<i>[sobbing]</i>

00:54:00.530 --> 00:54:02.573
[sobbing]

00:54:05.076 --> 00:54:10.331
[sobbing]
Tell Will it's not his fault.

00:54:10.415 --> 00:54:13.292
He's--he's gonna be--

00:54:13.376 --> 00:54:14.460
Don't talk.

00:54:14.544 --> 00:54:15.628
Just don't talk.

00:54:15.711 --> 00:54:17.046
Dad!

00:54:17.130 --> 00:54:19.590
[alarm beeping]

00:54:19.674 --> 00:54:21.968
I'm here.

00:54:22.051 --> 00:54:23.594
[alarm beeping]

00:54:23.678 --> 00:54:26.514
I'm here, baby.

00:54:26.597 --> 00:54:30.393
<i>We're here.
We're here.</i>

00:54:30.476 --> 00:54:32.395
We're right here.
[Crying]

00:54:32.478 --> 00:54:34.063
[alarm beeping]

00:54:36.649 --> 00:54:39.652
It's okay.
We're here.

00:54:39.735 --> 00:54:41.446
We're here.

00:54:41.529 --> 00:54:43.990
[crying]

00:54:45.283 --> 00:54:46.993
<i>[ominous music]</i>

00:54:48.119 --> 00:54:49.120
What's that?

00:54:49.203 --> 00:54:51.038
What is that?

00:54:51.122 --> 00:54:52.540
[gasps]

00:55:06.471 --> 00:55:08.055
It's okay!
Will!

00:55:08.139 --> 00:55:09.599
It's okay.
He's...

00:55:09.682 --> 00:55:12.393
He's with me.

00:55:13.811 --> 00:55:17.482
[gasping]

00:55:17.565 --> 00:55:20.568
<i>[sobbing]</i>

00:55:23.070 --> 00:55:27.575
<i>Danger, Will Robinson.</i>

00:55:27.658 --> 00:55:30.578
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

00:55:36.459 --> 00:55:38.294
Can you help her?

00:55:38.377 --> 00:55:40.630
Please?

00:55:40.713 --> 00:55:43.674
<i>[triumphant music]</i>

00:55:57.522 --> 00:56:00.024
[whimpering]

00:56:00.107 --> 00:56:03.152
[ice sizzling]

00:56:20.211 --> 00:56:22.588
[gasping]

00:56:26.008 --> 00:56:28.386
L9Â°tY0U-lgotyou.
