00:56:30.137 --> 00:56:32.557
Breathe.

00:56:32.640 --> 00:56:34.600
Breathe, baby.
Breathe.

00:56:34.684 --> 00:56:37.019
All: [laughing]

00:56:39.438 --> 00:56:40.648
It's okay. It's okay.

00:56:40.731 --> 00:56:46.028
[crying]

00:56:50.241 --> 00:56:53.077
Can you do something
so we don't freeze?

00:56:53.160 --> 00:56:56.080
<i>[hopeful music]</i>

00:57:32.617 --> 00:57:34.118
<i>[indistinct PA speaking]</i>

00:57:34.201 --> 00:57:37.580
<i>[alarms blaring]</i>

00:57:37.663 --> 00:57:39.624
<i>Thank you for
remaining calm.</i>

00:57:39.707 --> 00:57:41.125
Just make sure
it's over, right?

00:57:41.208 --> 00:57:42.585
[indistinct chatter]

00:57:42.668 --> 00:57:44.920
It's just
a temporary evacuation.

00:57:45.004 --> 00:57:48.090
I'm sure they'll have
the damage repaired soon.

00:57:48.174 --> 00:57:49.717
Where's Mary?
We need to stay together--

00:57:49.800 --> 00:57:52.261
Seems like an overreaction.

00:57:52.345 --> 00:57:55.139
<i>[speaking
in foreign language]</i>

00:57:55.222 --> 00:57:57.058
The sooner we seal
the breach, sooner we can

00:57:57.141 --> 00:58:00.144
get back to bitching
about being underpaid.

00:58:00.227 --> 00:58:02.021
We're being paid a fortune.

00:58:02.104 --> 00:58:03.189
Eh, that was before
we had a chance

00:58:03.272 --> 00:58:05.483
of being sucked out
into space.

00:58:07.610 --> 00:58:10.988
[alarm blaring]

00:58:11.072 --> 00:58:13.991
<i>[eerie music]</i>

00:58:14.075 --> 00:58:15.493
[people screaming]

00:58:15.576 --> 00:58:16.661
[laser shoots]
[explosion]

00:58:16.744 --> 00:58:18.663
Get down.
Get down!

00:58:18.746 --> 00:58:20.122
It's coming--
it's killing everybody!

00:58:20.206 --> 00:58:21.707
It?

00:58:21.791 --> 00:58:24.710
[panicked screams]

00:58:24.794 --> 00:58:28.005
[laser booming]

00:58:30.132 --> 00:58:31.467
[indistinct shouting]

00:58:31.550 --> 00:58:34.053
Get 'em off!
Get 'em off! Help me please!

00:58:34.136 --> 00:58:35.596
Oh God.

00:58:40.309 --> 00:58:41.310
Let me help you.

00:58:41.394 --> 00:58:42.687
Here.
Oh, thank you.

00:58:42.770 --> 00:58:44.605
Thank you.
Get your coat off.

00:58:44.689 --> 00:58:46.565
Can you walk?
No, I can't walk.

00:58:46.649 --> 00:58:48.234
Oh, I'm so sorry.

00:58:48.317 --> 00:58:51.153
Wait--wait.
What are you doing?

00:58:51.237 --> 00:58:52.697
I'm sorry.
What?

00:58:52.780 --> 00:58:54.490
What are you doing?

00:58:54.573 --> 00:58:56.575
Don't leave me here!

00:58:56.659 --> 00:58:58.160
Come back!

00:58:58.244 --> 00:59:00.996
<i>All resident colonists
please proceed</i>

00:59:01.080 --> 00:59:02.957
<i>to your assigned Jupiter pods.</i>

00:59:03.040 --> 00:59:04.709
We need to
get off this ship.

00:59:06.043 --> 00:59:07.712
No!

00:59:09.004 --> 00:59:10.798
The Jupiters are
for families only.

00:59:12.174 --> 00:59:14.218
Will you marry me?
flaughs]

00:59:16.095 --> 00:59:17.346
Come on.

00:59:17.430 --> 00:59:19.056
Hey.

00:59:19.140 --> 00:59:20.224
You fixing this?
Yeah.

00:59:20.307 --> 00:59:22.143
Yeah--yeah.
This one's yours?

00:59:22.226 --> 00:59:24.019
It's fixed.
It's good to go.

00:59:26.355 --> 00:59:27.356
[electronic beep]

00:59:27.440 --> 00:59:29.316
See?

00:59:29.400 --> 00:59:31.694
There you go.

00:59:31.777 --> 00:59:34.321
<i>All resident colonists
please proceed</i>

00:59:34.405 --> 00:59:36.657
<i>to your assigned Jupiter pods.</i>

00:59:36.741 --> 00:59:39.160
<i>Thank you for remaining calm.</i>

00:59:39.243 --> 00:59:41.537
There's always room
for a mechanic or two.

00:59:43.038 --> 00:59:46.292
Great! What about the rest
of your family?

00:59:46.375 --> 00:59:48.252
They won't be coming.

00:59:50.296 --> 00:59:51.297
Oh, sorry,
Miss...

00:59:51.380 --> 00:59:53.966
Doctor.

00:59:54.049 --> 00:59:56.844
Doctor Smith.

00:59:56.969 --> 01:00:00.055
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

01:00:04.143 --> 01:00:07.188
[explosions booming]

01:00:09.607 --> 01:00:12.193
[thrusters whoosh]

01:00:23.329 --> 01:00:25.956
[thrusters sputtering]

01:00:26.040 --> 01:00:27.625
[intense whooshing]

01:00:27.708 --> 01:00:29.960
[explosion]

01:00:30.044 --> 01:00:32.630
[gravity warbling]

